about.summary: A small INI library for Python.

name: inifile
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "inifile" %}
{% set version = "0.3" %}
{% set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{% set hash = "d0844a8db43f98ed514389b42b3e04243b5f694737feb24ce73906f6d928ed7d" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  {{ hash_type }}: {{ hash }}

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - inifile

about:
  home: https://github.com/mitsuhiko/python-inifile
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  summary: A small INI library for Python.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - goanpeca
